comments: Nurkic (POR) and Sabonis (IND) engage and disengage with one another along the perimeter.
Sabonis (IND) firms up in his screening position in Powell's (POR) path and absorbs the contact.
Powell (POR) brushes LeVert's (IND) left elbow and marginal contact occurs as LeVert passes.
Covington (POR) sets the pick on Holiday (IND), who is stationary, and does not deliver the contact. Covington and Holiday engage and disengage with one another thereafter.

Sabonis (IND) reaches his right hand forward and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Lillard's (POR) face. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Sabonis (IND) turns and delivers contact to Lillard's (POR) side after his gather, knocking Lillard off of his path toward the basket.

Sabonis' (IND) hand comes up toward Nurkic's (POR) arm and marginal contact occurs during the rebounding sequence. LeVert (IND) jumps toward the basket as he pursues the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Nurkic's left side.

Turner (IND) raises his right elbow up during the rebounding sequence and marginal contact occurs with the back of Nurkic's (POR) head. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.

Nurkic (POR) and Turner (IND) engage and disengage with one another after the shot is released. Nurkic makes clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental contact occurs with Turner's back thereafter.
Nurkic (POR) moves into McConnell's (IND) space and initiates contact across McConnell's arm after he secures the rebound.
Lillard's (POR) right forearm is extended forward toward McConnell's (IND) front and marginal contact occurs after McConnell's gather.
Sabonis (IND) and Nurkic (POR) engage with one another following the release of the shot attempt and incidental contact occurs as the rebound falls to the floor.
Sabonis (IND) grasps and then quickly releases Covington's (POR) left arm as he moves along the perimeter.
LeVert's (IND) hand is rested on McCollum's (POR) back during the drive and marginal contact occurs as McCollum releases away.
McCollum (POR) brings his off-arm toward LeVert's (IND) front and marginal contact occurs as McCollum naturally releases away.
Covington (POR) legally contests LeVert's (IND) jump shot attempt and any marginal contact that occurs is the result of LeVert extending his right leg outside the frame of his body.
Nance Jr. (POR) and Sabonis (IND) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Martin (IND) brings his left forearm toward Lillard's (POR) front and marginal contact occurs as Lillard's momentum carries him beyond the baseline during rebounding.
Holiday (IND) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Covington (POR) before incidental contact occurs.
Covington's (POR) arms extend forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Holiday's (IND) side as Covington sets the pick along the sideline.
Sabonis (IND) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
